      Clear ith bit:           x & ~(1 << i)
      Toggle ith bit:          x ^ (1 << i)
      Count set bits:          Brian Kernighan: while(x) { count++; x &= x-1; }
      Isolate rightmost 1:     x & (-x)
      Clear rightmost 1:       x & (x-1)
      Swap two numbers:        a^=b; b^=a; a^=b;
      XOR trick:               a^a = 0, a^0 = a

